Then the men came. They put me in

39:17.680 --> 39:22.200
prison. I died three months later.

39:23.080 --> 39:28.040
And then I came back home. Here. And

39:28.040 --> 39:31.380
I waited again. I waited for you.

39:32.080 --> 39:36.080
I love you, Ellen. I love you too,

39:36.380 --> 39:36.800
Matthew.

39:41.120 --> 39:45.960
Scene five. What is Brad going to do?

39:47.060 --> 39:51.000
It is dark. Brad is standing at the

39:51.000 --> 39:54.220
window of the room. Jerry comes in.

39:55.320 --> 39:58.740
Brad always has his back to Jerry in

39:58.740 --> 39:59.260
this scene.

40:01.240 --> 40:04.800
Do you want to die? Do you want

40:04.800 --> 40:05.900
to go to Ellen?

40:06.700 --> 40:12.080
Before today, the answer was yes. Matthew wanted

40:12.080 --> 40:15.000
to die and go to be with Ellen.

40:15.960 --> 40:20.540
Do you understand that? Yes. But Matthew is

40:20.540 --> 40:23.360
dead and I am Brad now.

40:24.200 --> 40:28.640
And what does Brad want? I don't know.

40:29.740 --> 40:33.200
I'm thinking. Is there a train from here

40:33.200 --> 40:34.240
to London tomorrow?

40:34.860 --> 40:39.160
Yes. We can put our bicycles on the

40:39.160 --> 40:42.520
train. We can get the next plane back

40:42.520 --> 40:43.180
to America.

40:44.020 --> 40:47.640
Do you want to do that? I don't

40:47.640 --> 40:50.740
know. I'm going to tell you tomorrow.

40:53.720 --> 40:59.760
Scene six. In love with a ghost. The

40:59.760 --> 41:03.760
next day, Brad and Jerry are in the

41:03.760 --> 41:06.980
street. Jerry has two bags.

41:07.860 --> 41:13.200
Mrs. Finch is there too. You must leave

41:13.200 --> 41:14.960
then. A week early.

41:15.680 --> 41:20.980
Yes. I'm sorry. Oh, hello. It's the American

41:20.980 --> 41:23.620
boys. Are you going home to America?

41:24.520 --> 41:28.840
Jerry's going home, Mrs. Morgan. I'm staying here

41:28.840 --> 41:32.420
at the hotel. I'm going to live here.

41:33.240 --> 41:33.500
Always.

41:34.400 --> 41:38.860
Brad, do you want to do this? Think

41:38.860 --> 41:42.940
about Davis TV. What are you going to

41:42.940 --> 41:44.240
do here in England?

41:44.940 --> 41:49.460
I don't know. But yes, Davis TV needs

41:49.460 --> 41:53.420
a good man. My dad worked for years

41:53.420 --> 41:54.740
for Davis TV.

41:55.560 --> 41:58.780
But now it has a good man, Jerry.

42:00.020 --> 42:06.460
You. Me? Oh, thank you, Brad. That's okay.

42:07.320 --> 42:08.260
I'm happy.

42:09.000 --> 42:13.140
I'm in love. She waited for me and

42:13.140 --> 42:17.600
now I'm here. I'm never going to leave

42:17.600 --> 42:18.640
her again.

42:47.000 --> 42:48.400
I'm not going to leave her alone.

